Thunderpants is a comedy about a boy who farts all the time. It turns out he was born with two stomachs that produce enough gas even to fart him into space.

Personally, I don?t think this is a funny film. But it?s a request, so I made a small DivX from my original Australian dvd I got for present a few years back.

It?s not a screwball slap-stick comedy, it has more of a matter-of-fact wry smile approach to it, so the format itself resembles any major studio?s well-made sensible family comedy intended for the average viewer, except for the theme.

It did win the Lucas award in 2002, though.
